title: Ep. 739 Hidden Bombshells in the Leak Investigation
description:
Summary:
In this episode I address the explosive information contained in the court paperwork in the leak investigation. I also address President Trump’s comments at the G-7 and the recent decision by the DOJ that could decimate Obamacare.
 
News Picks:
This piece destroys the ongoing, disgraceful media spin about Spygate.
 
The DOJ is still withholding documents from congressional oversight. 
 
This piece debunks another desperate liberal economic narrative. 
 
Obamacare is in deep trouble due to these recent decisions by the DOJ.
 
Obamacare is driving premiums up dramatically.
 
Another Obama administration scandal brewing at the National Archives.
 
The court documents from the leak investigation are interesting. Pay attention to the dates.
